infos.urlText: The Gibbons Street entrance to Redfern Station will be closed until the end of November.
infos.content: You can continue to use Lawson Street concourse and Platform 10 to enter and exit the station. If you have a mobility aid such as wheelchair or scooter, and are travelling to or from Platform 6/7, please use the new ramp at Lawson Street. If you need assistance, please speak to Redfern Station staff, or call 9379 1398.
infos.subtitle: The Gibbons Street entrance to Redfern Station will be closed until the end of November.
